HOUSE COMMITTEES

WAYS AND MEANS

 

JURISDICTION: All matters directly and principally relating to the fiscal, monetary and financial affairs of the national government including tariff, taxation, revenues, borrowing, credit and bonded indebtedness.

CHAIRPERSON :

Salceda, Joey Sarte

District Representative
Albay, 2nd District
